scenario_text.value: Oh no... Is this it for me...?
What is it, Saki? What’s wrong?!

Please, Doctor... At least until the end of
the camping trip...
Thank goodness... You with us, now?

Wh-what...? Takuma and Agumon are here, too?
What am I...?
Oh! Um, did I...did I say anything, or...?
Oh, uh, yeah? That’s fine, then...

(Is Saki hiding something? I admit I’m
curious, but more importantly...)

I’m glad you’re all right, Saki, but where’s
Floramon?

Oh, the thing is... She started bad-mouthing
me out of nowhere.
(I knew it, a fake Floramon appeared, too.)
